{
  "texts": [
    "The recommendation service facilitates users' access to relevant digital content, including news, vlogs, photos, commercials, and more.",
    "Hence, personalized recommender systems have recently gained increased attention because of their functionality in providing user-defined content.",
    "Algorithms used in such systems analyze specific users' usage behavior to predict and deliver recommendations.",
    "Since there are many social media users, and this number is increasing with time, metadata is also rising.",
    "This vast number of metadata enhances the performance of personalized recommendation systems (Lu et al., 2015; Wang et al., 2013)."
  ]
}